data.description: Welcome to this charming 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in the heart of Maricopa! This spacious and versatile floor plan offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience, making it ideal for next-gen living or accommodating guests with 4 bedrooms upstairs including a large master suite with tub/shower combo and 1 bedroom and bath on the lower level.  Cathedral ceilings in the entry, 2 car garage.  Solar panels are leased with a water softener system as well.  Come see this home while it lasts.
